entries.title_d: Destroy the Prison Break Shuttle that is attempting to leave the Dathomir system. A vessel has left the planet's surface. It is believed to be containing more Imperial prison officers. They must be eliminated for their failure in their duty.
entries.title: Dathomir System: Destroy the Prison Break Shuttle
entries.split_quest_alert: Alert! Another vessel detected attempting to leave Dathomir's surface. Intercept and destroy.
entries.quest_target_d: Intercept and destroy the prison break vessel before it can leave the system. The officers on board cannot be allowed to leave the system.
entries.quest_location_d: Remain in the Dathomir system and intercept the Prison Break Shuttle.
entries.quest_escort_d: Destroy the Coynite guards that are traveling with the prison break shuttle.
entries.failed_escape: This is a disaster. You let the ship jump out of the sector. Make a full report of your failure to your superior.
entries.destroy_escort: You destoyed the ship leaving Dathomir but there are still members of its escort remaining. No one is to get out alive.
entries.assassinate_success: Very well done, pilot. But there is more work yet to be done. Stand by.
entries.arrival_phase_2: Vessel attempting to leave Dathomir has arrived in ordit. Destroy that ship and every ship with it.
entries.arrival_phase_1: We are tracking the vessels departure point. That ship is not to leave the sector. Destroy it as soon as it enters orbit.
